## Backups with Garage

```
CloudNativePG (WAL + daily base backup)
  └─► Garage S3 bucket (s3://postgres-backups/, local-path)
        └─► [snapshots every 6h]
              └─► NFS → /vault/garage/ on dorne (ZFS)
```

