## Backups with VolSync and Garage

```
Longhorn PVCs
  └─► VolSync ReplicationSource (Longhorn snapshots every 6h)
        └─► Garage S3 bucket (s3://volsync-backup/app/, local-path
              └─► [snapshots entire hot tier every 6h]
                    └─► NFS → /vault/garage/ on dorne (ZFS)
```

# ZFS backups

```
ZFS datasets machine 1
  └─► Sanoid snapshots
  └─► Syncoid → ZFS machine 2
        └─► Kopia → Backblaze B2
```

